def fibonacciSum(n):
    a = 1
    b = 1
    sum = 0
    while a < n:
        if (a % 3 == 0 or a % 5 == 0) and (a % 10 == 3 or a % 10 == 7):
            sum += a
        temp = a
        a = b
        b = temp + b
    return sum
